0.1.2.name: monokai-dark-plus
0.1.2.description: A dark (plus) monokai theme for language-babel
0.1.2.readme:
# Dark (plus) Monokai theme

A dark monokai syntax theme for [Atom](http://atom.io/).

Fork fom [monokai-dark](https://github.com/james2doyle/atom-monokai-dark). Originally converted from [monokai](https://github.com/kevinsawicki/monokai) which in turn came from the [TextMate](http://www.monokai.nl/blog/wp-content/asdev/Monokai.tmTheme) theme using the [TextMate bundle converter](http://atom.io/docs/latest/converting-a-text-mate-theme).

![](https://raw.github.com/james2doyle/atom-monokai-dark-plus/master/screenshot.png)
